Anisible sample file

Hereâ€™s a sample Ansible playbook file that installs Apache HTTP server on a Linux system (e.g., Ubuntu or CentOS), starts the service, and ensures it's enabled on boot.

---
- name: Install and start Apache web server
  hosts: webservers
  become: true   # Run with sudo/root privileges

  tasks:
    - name: Install Apache (Ubuntu)
      apt:
        name: apache2
        state: present
      when: ansible_os_family == "Debian"

    - name: Install Apache (CentOS)
      yum:
        name: httpd
        state: present
      when: ansible_os_family == "RedHat"

    - name: Start Apache service
      service:
        name: "{{ 'apache2' if ansible_os_family == 'Debian' else 'httpd' }}"
        state: started
        enabled: true
